{
  "page": "Orivel the Open-Handed",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/50px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/75px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/100px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Orivel<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Open-Handed</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/50px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/75px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/100px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nOrivel the Open-Handed</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Ser <b>Orivel the Open-Handed</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> at an unknown time.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orivel_the_Open-Handed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>He is remembered as a knight who shamed the white cloak of the Kingsguard. History remembers him as a coward.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orivel_the_Open-Handed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jaime</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Greycloak\" title=\"Gyles Greycloak\">Gyles Greycloak</a>? Orivel the Open-Handed?<br />\n<b>Loras</b>: Gyles was a traitor, Orivel a coward. Men who shamed the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">white cloak</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orivel_the_Open-Handed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Jaime II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403112616\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.070 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.259 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 502/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10522/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5961/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 538/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 805/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  247.551      1 -total\n 96.50%  238.883      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.65%  236.792      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.87%   24.435     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.09%   12.593      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.14%    5.297      2 Template:Ref\n  